title: Will I get CSE in first round with rank 856?

comments.body: Might be tough in first round, but surely in second round you will get.
Hey I got a rank of 912 is it the same for me or no?
As far as I remember CSE closed at 1050 or something in second round for Ring Road Campus and 2k for EC campus.
Unlikely in RR campus, but you might get at EC campus
Last year it was 1057 in RR campus, in PESSAT 1st round it was 659 tho..

thank you, and so ill have to wait for second round? 

also if u have the last year cutoffs could you please send it to me?
